    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/dc27d19d939aaf185e88533f4fc08396.avif?t=1764031972\" width=628 height=86 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/648c8f51a144027900f1b749018ef92c.poster.avif?t=1764031972\" width=628 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/648c8f51a144027900f1b749018ef92c.webm?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/648c8f51a144027900f1b749018ef92c.mp4?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>冰海孤翼的舞台，乃是6500年后的地球。大冰河时代的来临让地球化作一颗巨大的雪球，全世界都被寒冰所覆盖。生命只能在厚重冰层下的海洋里寻求生路。<br><br>这片海洋有着覆盖着植被的冰壳天空、会自己发光点缀着海底的鱼类。而你便是讴歌着全新的生命黄金时代之繁荣的物种，鸟类的末裔——图艾。图艾拥有高度的智慧，以及异常发达的代谢能力。它们的历史横跨数千万年，只要繁育丰饶生态体系的大冰河期——“永冬”能够持续下去。图艾种族的繁荣便可如磐石般坚牢存续。<br><br>而玩家便要作为一只图艾，直面这片永冬正在迎来的威胁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/053ea78b147f1558906a099c6224ef84.poster.avif?t=1764031972\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/053ea78b147f1558906a099c6224ef84.webm?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/053ea78b147f1558906a099c6224ef84.mp4?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/47753d4166e6e64194b59b4f38c35045.poster.avif?t=1764031972\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/47753d4166e6e64194b59b4f38c35045.webm?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/47753d4166e6e64194b59b4f38c35045.mp4?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《冰海孤翼》是一款实时战斗的动作游戏，释放图艾从鸟类和恐龙血脉中所继承而来的力量，运用近程，远程攻击和特殊技能击退来犯的强敌，并用其独有的能力控制冷与热的变化。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/5eb5045445e599219ffb4fc4b6aafdff.poster.avif?t=1764031972\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/5eb5045445e599219ffb4fc4b6aafdff.webm?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/5eb5045445e599219ffb4fc4b6aafdff.mp4?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/c996f47a2cae869cb0bd0cc90eda7b3b.poster.avif?t=1764031972\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/c996f47a2cae869cb0bd0cc90eda7b3b.webm?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/c996f47a2cae869cb0bd0cc90eda7b3b.mp4?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过超临界水通道施展高速游泳法、瞬间生成结晶打造一次性的利刃、拥有操控热量能力的图艾可以自由施展组合各种各样的能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/b8f8830c716802b762501248e447bb5c.poster.avif?t=1764031972\" width=628 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/b8f8830c716802b762501248e447bb5c.webm?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/b8f8830c716802b762501248e447bb5c.mp4?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/a8146850de1a05aab657f80be38d7675.poster.avif?t=1764031972\" width=628 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/a8146850de1a05aab657f80be38d7675.webm?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/a8146850de1a05aab657f80be38d7675.mp4?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>6500万年后的海洋中存在着极为独特的动植物群。你可以看到茂盛生长在冰层天空上的草原、遍布海底的好热鱼群、以及摆脱了重力束缚的巨大化鳄鱼等等。探索这片冰层下的海洋，发现更多令人惊叹的生物吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/f3fc3a46b011c82f06cd0e2676d1fbfb.poster.avif?t=1764031972\" width=628 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/f3fc3a46b011c82f06cd0e2676d1fbfb.webm?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2052300/extras/f3fc3a46b011c82f06cd0e2676d1fbfb.mp4?t=1764031972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《冰海孤翼》支持NVIDIA RTX技术。拥有光线追踪和DLSS的加持，主要角色更是用了8K材质贴图。在4K分辨率下体验这个遥远未来的地球吧！",
